{"tid":1634344,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對家又玩兩極分化︰極端和理非︰休息八日、極端勇武︰爆哂所有舗","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:38:38.000Z","uid":196430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb3165f5fa05fdfe2c9e335ac9e227fda1caaaf","tid":1634344,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:33:09.000Z","msg":"識睇就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時睇下對家點帶風向，都不失為一種樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同你講啦，八日後通過人權及民主法案係假，八日後只係美國國會復會，通過好可能要月底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於爆哂所有舗？郁啲就裝修？口角都神獸？傻嘅都知係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係想破壞大家辛苦達到嘅共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂，中庸之道是好東西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將連登風向從中間解讀，就係對家最驚嘅行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n換言之，和理非要做嘅唔係咩休息，而係全面開工進場，擠提、搶糧、罷工、行為藝術、裝置藝術、文宣、論述咩撚都要。總之就係繼續將香港死城化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而前線就要限制行動範圍，公眾已經接受嘅可以繼續玩，有爭議嘅放火可以停一停，暫時無需要擴大戰場住，否則和理非抗爭者無空間參與，亦唔係一件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家急嘅係中共，而唔係我哋，十月中貿易談判、十月底人權法同國內四中全會、十一月初英國脫歐後又話會搞人權法，我地保持軍紀，贏撚硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108494a159fa3de446de45b6f9508c935b2614d1","tid":1634344,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c61d01ad66068af4950cc81af2903a061fc890f","tid":1634344,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h=bfdca82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標一、哂馬</span></strong></span><br />\n由於警狗唔再批不反，即使批左亦會製造衝突。<br />\n為左令和理非可以舒舒服服地出返黎，展示人數同民意，<br />\n所以就利用黃店門外既人龍，製造畫面同話題吸引媒體注意。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標二、支持黃色經濟</span></span></strong><br />\n依幾個月生意難免受影響，加上可能被藍絲杯葛，<br />\n良心黃店係好需要大家支持。<br />\n最實際既支持當然就係拎銀包出黎，入錢入錢入錢！<br />\n另外參考連登既食評，由於良心經營既關係，黃店食物質素一般都偏高，<br />\n絕對係win win雙贏！<br />\n<br />\n------------國際文宣------------<br />\n請將買返黎既貨物/食物/單據同排隊盛況<br />\n一齊用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#Buy4HK</span></span></strong><br />\n放上IG, Twitter, reddit"},{"pid":"966156b044caacf6d095936999622f5b509ac55e","tid":1634344,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}